Fix 2 — write_controller_vars_file()

Do not set GENERATED_GROUP_VARS_SOURCE_FILE inside the function anymore.

Inside write_controller_vars_file(), remove these lines if they exist:

local generated_group_vars_tmp=""
generated_group_vars_tmp="$(make_temp_file)"
GENERATED_GROUP_VARS_SOURCE_FILE="${generated_group_vars_tmp}"
: > "${generated_group_vars_tmp}"

Then near the top of the function, make it look like this:

write_controller_vars_file() {
  local file
  local repo_vars_file=""
  file="$(make_temp_file)"
  [[ -n "${GENERATED_GROUP_VARS_SOURCE_FILE:-}" ]] || fail "GENERATED_GROUP_VARS_SOURCE_FILE must be set before write_controller_vars_file"
  : > "${file}"
  : > "${GENERATED_GROUP_VARS_SOURCE_FILE}"
  # Do not let group_vars_defaults inject generated bootstrap data into
  # workstation_defaults.yml. Bootstrap now writes generated group vars directly to:
  #   collections-hub/ansible/group_vars/all/aerolit_bootstrap_generated.yml
  {
    echo "group_vars_defaults_manage_nfs_mount_defaults: false"
    echo "group_vars_defaults_manage_scalar_values: false"
    echo "group_vars_defaults_manage_extra_blocks: false"
    echo
  } >> "${file}"

Then at the bottom of write_controller_vars_file(), make sure this line uses the parent-created file:

write_bootstrap_generated_group_vars_file "${GENERATED_GROUP_VARS_SOURCE_FILE}" "${repo_vars_file}"

not this:

write_bootstrap_generated_group_vars_file "${generated_group_vars_tmp}" "${repo_vars_file}"

Then keep:

echo "${file}"

as the last line of the function.

⸻

Why this fixes it

The temp file path now exists in the parent shell before this runs:

CONTROLLER_VARS_FILE="$(write_controller_vars_file)"

Even though the function runs in a subshell, it writes actual content to the temp file path that the parent already knows about. After the function returns, this works:

install_bootstrap_generated_group_vars_file "${GENERATED_GROUP_VARS_SOURCE_FILE}"

That should stop the “source file was not set” failure and let it write:

collections-hub/ansible/group_vars/all/aerolit_bootstrap_generated.yml